data.description: Situated on a large lot of .31 acres, there is plenty of space for outdoor activities. With 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home offers ample space for the whole family. The property also offers RV parking and lots of parking space for multiple vehicles. Both the front and backyard are fully fenced. Additionally, a new concrete patio slab has been installed.  This whole house features a 1-year-old water filter and new flooring in living room and laundry room. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Yakima house your new home!
